perf: optimize property map for mobile (2.3 MB to 50-200 KB)

Replaced the 2.3 MB PNG with optimized variants generated from the
same source: WebP at 800/1200/1672 widths (51/112/198 KB) and JPEG
at 800/1672 widths (66/261 KB) as the fallback. Switched the markup
to a picture element with srcset and sizes so each device only loads
the variant it needs. The full-size link target stays as the largest
JPEG so opening in a new tab works in any browser.

Mobile gets the 51 KB WebP, desktop gets the 198 KB WebP, ancient
browsers get the JPEG fallback. ~92% bandwidth reduction on modern
clients.

